         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="6d1276f7-bd9e-402b-b8d8-4bb1d5e76434"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="underline">
                     <content styleCode="bold">DESCRIPTION:</content>
                  </content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Ovaprim® is a liquid peptide preparation that contains an analog of salmon gonadotropin releasing hormone (sGnRHa) and a brain neurotransmitter (dopamine) inhibitor. The sGnRHa in Ovaprim® elicits the release of stored gonadotropins from the pituitary. The dopamine inhibitor (domperidone) serves to remove other inhibition of GnRH release. Release of stored pituitary gonadotropins may aid spawning by stimulating ovulation and spermiation in sexually mature fish.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20260413"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="03e88b6b-d0a4-40d4-97f8-7da461c4ea7a"/>
               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Injectable Solution<br/>Spawning aid for intraperitoneal or intramuscular injection<br/>
                     <content styleCode="bold">FOR USE IN FINFISH BROODSTOCK ONLY</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">LEGAL STATUS -- In order to be legally marketed, a new animal drug intended for a minor species must be Approved, Conditionally Approved, or Indexed by the Food and Drug Administration.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">THIS PRODUCT IS INDEXED – MIF 900-001. Extra-label use is prohibited.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">THIS PRODUCT IS NOT TO BE USED IN ANIMALS INTENDED FOR USE AS FOOD FOR HUMANS OR FOOD PRODUCING ANIMALS.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">It is a violation of federal law to use this product in a manner other than as directed in the labeling.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20260220"/>
            </section>
         </component>
